    <p>JRG and PP conceived the idea of modelling RNA-seq count data using PT family of distributions. ME programmed the recursive algorithm to compute PT probability distribution, performed simulation studies, and created the R package jointly with JRG and RC. PP and JRG proposed the statistical test for detecting DE genes. DG preprocessed the RNA-seq data. RC, ME and JRG analysed the data and wrote the paper. The project was supervised by JRG. All authors read and approved the final manuscript.</p>
  </sec>
